OL,6, Graffiti scrawled on a rainbow road
OL,7, crossing in Bristol proves why such
OL,8, efforts to support the LGBTQ+ community
OL,9, are needed, a campaigner has said.
OL,11,FThe puffin crossing, incorporating the
OL,12,FPride Progress Flag, was installed on
OL,13,FWine street in Bristol on 30 June.
OL,15,FLess than 48 hours later it had been
OL,16,Fdefaced.
OL,18,FThe crossing has now been cleaned.
OL,19,FBristol Pride organiser Daryn Carter
OL,20,Fsaid he had been disappointed but not
OL,21,Fsurprised by the graffiti.
